        <div class="content">
          
          <div id="upage_title">Users</div>
          <div id="uads">


<center>

</center>

          </div>
          <p>This page lists the open source projects, people and companies using ServiceMix. Please add yourself to this list - click on the edit button on the bottom right of this page or get <a href="How+does+the+website+work" title="How does the website work">more help</a>.</p>

<div class="section_3"><h3><a name="Users-OpenSourceProjectsusingServiceMix"></a>Open Source Projects using ServiceMix</h3>

<ul>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://geronimo.apache.org/">Apache Geronimo</a></span> uses ServiceMix as its JBI container and component suite.</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://celtix.objectweb.org/">Celtix</a></span> uses ServiceMix as its JBI container and component suite.</li>
</ul>


